{
  "description": "A close-up shot of the center of a white tulip, showcasing its delicate petals and vibrant yellow stamen. The petals are slightly curved and appear almost translucent, with subtle shadows adding depth. The stamen is a bright, golden yellow, creating a strong contrast against the white petals. The image is focused on the flower's reproductive parts, hinting at themes of nature and growth. A dark green background provides a stark contrast, isolating the tulip and making its colors pop. The lighting is soft but highlights the textures of the petals and the details of the stamen.",
